× Beauty<\/strong><br>We have always wanted to create a model of electric tricycles that has sufficient performance but also combines beauty and safety. The undulation of the lines on the frame is a nice point. Our design team took the mountains and rivers of various places as references and spent half a year designing the main frame of the MaxZ series of electric tricycles. Although the design effect is beyond imagination, conventional production methods seem unable to perfectly realize the design for these electric tricycles — some of the beauty and safety would need to be sacrificed, which is definitely not what we want. So we decided to use a more advanced one-piece molding process at a higher cost to achieve the most perfect safety and beauty of the design for our electric tricycles.","pc_margin_top":"0px","pc_margin_bottom":"0px","mb_margin_top":"0px","mb_margin_bottom":"0px"}},"four_squares_icon_XCNnYR":{"type":"fourSquares_icon","blocks":{"four_squares_icon_box_DYqbke":{"type":"fourSquaresIconBox","settings":{"icon_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_c5b14fbe-2376-4460-ad67-3a97b4401d8c.png","icon_header":"48V 20Ah","icon_desc":"SAMSUNG Battery<br>With UL Certification"}},"four_squares_icon_box_Gcfkex":{"type":"fourSquaresIconBox","settings":{"icon_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_3a2be8c9-5037-40d3-bbed-571bc49f7397.png","icon_header":"750W","icon_desc":"Maxfoot High Power Motor<br>1400W Peak Power"}},"four_squares_icon_box_CxKaAm":{"type":"fourSquaresIconBox","settings":{"icon_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_9d7fb959-af50-4d95-901a-cb8b192a5572.png","icon_header":"90N.m","icon_desc":"Powerful<br>Motor Torque"}},"four_squares_icon_box_KWY9cY":{"type":"fourSquaresIconBox","settings":{"icon_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_7e26f46e-e663-48ac-81dd-85e25223d397.png","icon_header":"300 Lbs","icon_desc":"Maximum<br>Load"}}},"block_order":["four_squares_icon_box_DYqbke","four_squares_icon_box_Gcfkex","four_squares_icon_box_CxKaAm","four_squares_icon_box_KWY9cY"],"cu